paper_metadata.extraction_summary: Extracted information on the KCNH2 variant A990G, including penetrance data and individual records.

individual_records.evidence_sentence: The proband, a 46-year-old man, was admitted to the hospital for a recurrent fever, which induced a type 2 BrS ECG in the V2 lead.

functional_data.summary: The variant was predicted to be deleterious with more than eight bioinformatic tools.

variants.population_frequency: Absent from controls in ExAC and gnomAD
key_quotes: The novel c.2969C > G variant in the KCNH2 gene was classified as being likely pathogenic according to the ACMG.

extraction_metadata.notes: Extracted all relevant data for the KCNH2 variant A990G.
